{
  "stem": "18470.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 554.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I do remember visiting my grandparents in Niederzissen, and another set of grandparents in Gau-Odernheim.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were big trips.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were also a couple hours by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, I-- I don't remember very much of it, other than sort of a bucolic form of life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in a family home, which had a beautiful garden that was rather tranquil.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- um-- we had lots of relatives all the time coming to visit and stay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember our house, our home, as being lively, festive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the Pesach celebration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was-- that was even more impressive than going to synagogue on Rosh Hashanah or Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my father and grandfather would get dressed in their-- what they call their sargenes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sargenes is the Greek word for the robe you wear upon your ultimate retirement and death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "White robe, and they would sit there with their slippers on, ready to go on the exodus again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then during the day, they would dress up very festively in top hats, as they would go to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Seder was long, and was noisy, with family and relatives coming to visit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember-- I remember my father and grandfather leading the service at the table, and my asking the four questions, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was an only child, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I was the oldest grandchild, right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lived in Gau-Odernheim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my family was split.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Gerson family who were the proprietors of the house in Oberwesel, and the family into which my father married, lived in Oberwesel for more than 400 years.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can assert that, because the gravestones in the friedhof, the Jewish cemetery, go back by family lines at least 400 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
